description: Based on weather in Seattle, WA this skill recommends what to wear for Men. It even suggests accessories. NOTE: Skill is supported only for Seattle region and recommends only Men's clothing for now.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Dress me what to wear
Alexa, ask Dress me what to wear now
name: Dress Me
shortDescription: Based on weather in Seattle, WA this skill suggests what to wear for Men.
